\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {5}{\ignorespaces Genome hot-reload sequence diagram. The EvoClaw server triggers a genome mutation, the kernel pauses the agent, atomically swaps the genome pages (using copy-on-write), registers the new genome on ClawChain, and resumes the agent with preserved state. Total downtime: $<$5ms.}}{11}{figure.caption.6}\protected@file@percent }
